reviews.review_text: double dipped gratefuldead gotta like two encores. Jerry is really mellow in this show, but i like that. things get stretched out. Slow Miss1/2step but smooth and laid back in a real good way. Persian?  Nice spooky space in the Other one, i enjoy this stuff. Pretty good sound, slightly odd mix at times, but less is more.
